history.content:
If you plan to study abroad in Summer 2019, Fall 2019, or the full 2019-20 academic year, you have paperwork due to the Study Abroad office on the last day of classes. Please plan ahead to schedule an advising appointment early and complete this form ahead of time. We will not be available to accommodate last-minute requests.

If you plan to take major courses abroad, there is a process that requires faculty review: https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/study-abroad
history.subject: UCEAP Academic Planning Form due Friday, May 3 (for Summer & Fall/Year 2019-20)
